::Hot Rod::

He waited in his IGL room, for the next match. He was lucky he hadn't
been kicked out. But he had no choice but to kill his opponent, if he
hadn't, he would be dead now. He wondered about his next match. Would he
see Epyon?

::Epyon::

He stood prepared for his next battle. He knew not to expect the ease he
found in his last match, but he was ready.

(KSL, this free for all, do all of the round 1 winners just go at it?
And will you officialy start it?)

::DrillBit/KitKat2::

They both watched as the drones worked at extracting Foxfingers spark.
DrillBit chuckled and KitKat had an evil smile on her face.

(I might have missed the post but I dont remember a reply on this
earlier Cyberwolf. Could you either post or repost on this? Thanks.)

::Skyburst::

He finally arrived at Autobot HQ, although a little ahead of his escort.
He opened a comm link.
"This is the Autobot Skyburst, I have arrived. Could you please let me
in?"

::Prowl::

He walked around Maximal City. He missed Iron Raptor, and wished she
would return. He was also thinking about his new position as Maximal
Commander.

(I dont know what Prowl was doing last, so I'm starting off like that.
Also I need to know what the majority of Maximals are doing and what is
happaning at Maximal City. With my other Maxi's at IGL I had not been
following that.)
